data.description: Welcome home to this better than new 3 bed/2 bath/ 2 car garage located in the well desired Paloma neighborhood.  This stunning 1 story offers a modern and inviting living space. As you step inside, you're greeted by a spacious foyer, an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the kitchen to the living room. The backyard is a peaceful retreat with a recently installed custom wooden deck.  Minutes from Randolph AFB, Fort Sam and great shopping emtertainment!  This one wont last, schedule your showing now!!!
